{"tid":661524,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"孤僻嘅性格會令人錯過好多嘢","createTime":"2018-05-11T15:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T18:40:26.000Z","uid":99024,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"78e383c8d437d904b496581292bb832456b8ebe3","tid":661524,"uid":99024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:39:19.000Z","msg":"孤僻是一種孤寡怪僻、而不合群的人格表現。這類型的人經常獨往獨來、離群索居，對他人懷有厭煩、戒備和鄙視的心理；凡事與己無關、漠不關心，一副自我禁錮的樣子；如果與人交往，也缺少熱情和活力，顯得漫不經心、敷衍了事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底係由幾時開始我變到越嚟越孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢種性格令到我無論係感情、工作上都受到好多挫折<br />\n<br />\n不停咁被人誤會，誤解<br />\n冇辦法將自己心入面嘅諗法好好咁傳達比其他人<br />\n慢慢去到連朋友都識唔到<br />\n連身邊嘅人都話我冷漠，甚至冇禮貌<br />\n唔識同人交往嘅基本禮儀<br />\n<br />\n其實我真係唔想咁<br />\n只係有時真係覺得好攰<br />\n與其每日戴住個面具做人<br />\n寧願將自己同外界隔絕仲舒服<br />\n<br />\n矛盾嘅係自己另一方面又好想作出改變<br />\n但係即使改善左一啲面表上嘅嘢<br />\n內心世界依然都係孤獨<br />\n<br />\n到最後發覺自己根本冇做到任何改變<br />\n都係繼續被人誤解，嫌棄<br />\n慢慢咁變成離群嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oYw4uH80gcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoYw4uH80gcw&d=6BqVB6%2Ff04Cdty6UfhOPLZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3a06c455\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oYw4uH80gcw</a>"},{"pid":"07ee5d401a2214102d0da0c321c351e54a3123d9","tid":661524,"uid":102179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下點俾人誤解呢？"},{"pid":"bc728d66f767cbfb5d0b187814b828278bc0fadf","tid":661524,"uid":180716,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我明 黎緊諗住改變下自己  做返自己  諗真啲自己孤僻都係驚講錯野  驚人地點睇我  慢慢先開始變到咁"},{"pid":"1cc48f87d866fc4e0e2f0e5198084d3b01e58e42","tid":661524,"uid":99024,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bc728d66f767cbfb5d0b187814b828278bc0fadf","tid":661524,"uid":180716,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我明 黎緊諗住改變下自己  做返自己  諗真啲自己孤僻都係驚講錯野  驚人地點睇我  慢慢先開始變到咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"我都係 好在意其他人點睇我"},{"pid":"f8f66dac4b97b16b5f10a90542b4390eb6907d0b","tid":661524,"uid":108199,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"就算比人當毒撚都唔理<br />\n我行我素幾自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134877665566f02a16930dc7d50afb6589ae7baa","tid":661524,"uid":180948,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:05:42.000Z","msg":"岩阿 我都係 遇到鍾意既人都唔識點爭取機會 唔識表達"},{"pid":"22daa45fea1e0ae6e88f3e068fe04e94d53f401a","tid":661524,"uid":34768,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:05:48.000Z","msg":"一樣情況<br />\n雖然知道問題出係邊，但改唔到"},{"pid":"32a4d770dd7412ef68e9ac5ae9de56751ea44b89","tid":661524,"uid":116718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"critical hit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad33eef4cc1afb090dcd098375f52d45ec0e67da","tid":661524,"uid":61758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"我想㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ffaab681840d6c9739d1c4e995bc52a3f1708c","tid":661524,"uid":104499,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"sad but true 有時連比人誤會左都唔會想去解釋"},{"pid":"2039777899c18df9643fd9f61dc49ce4c0861764","tid":661524,"uid":99024,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:18:32.000Z","msg":"有時係冇機會解釋<br />\n有時解釋左只會越描越黑<br />\n有時知道其他人點睇你嘅時候已經太遲"},{"pid":"046a2b7bfcc742c26b27bd4b4a1d3747f8e10e88","tid":661524,"uid":36539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本諗住今年踏前一步改變吓自己嘅生活模式, 反而變得更加孤僻錯過咗好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674ad7578cf45baee192fc2b4498f2ead0bb4fe5","tid":661524,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4d6fd7a8c1268da4adf92724986132398061215","tid":661524,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"我唔想孤僻架 環境做成"},{"pid":"b57454ba5770bd2e4e430d575586522754d9d3f0","tid":661524,"uid":145618,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"以前性格好孤僻 講緊係完全唔同人講嘢 自閉咁<br />\n直到高中識到班朋友先叫好啲 跟住都好地地<br />\n但直到Asso最後呢個學期發生得太多事 又變番以前咁<br />\n見到識既人都扮睇唔到 有時真係覺得自己痴撚線"},{"pid":"3bed12394cb7e0190ae473a16bf939ca653545e0","tid":661524,"uid":99024,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f4d6fd7a8c1268da4adf92724986132398061215","tid":661524,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"我唔想孤僻架 環境做成"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"性格好多時候係因為一個人嘅成長經歷同埋身邊嘅環境造成<br />\n<br />\n其實我細個嗰時係一個外向、活潑同鍾意表現自己嘅人嚟<br />\n<br />\n可能因為太在意人哋對我嘅睇法<br />\n漸漸咁變得鍾意收埋自己"},{"pid":"73eacb68a210be7d661bc492a758189c28cbf634","tid":661524,"uid":75768,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"唉，我份人都好孤僻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錯過既人和事真係太多啦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n成日好灰好自卑，又玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係人前又扮冇野，扮活躍去迎合下人，一個人一靜落黎就厭世樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4151d71f2cf93ff5fa5b821f2716b5480153ab","tid":661524,"uid":28624,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"屌 講得勁中<br />\n錯過左好多好多野<br />\n好想改變<br />\n<br />\n唯獨排外既性格一定要保留<br />\n係保障自己利益既絕佳方法<br />\n以前就係太易將自己個心交俾其他人<br />\n到頭來根本冇人當你係自己人 仲俾人出賣"},{"pid":"7f5d972327d419dd4558